page.title: 1020TH CENTURY CHILDREN.
page.content: {Myself.}My name is Samantha Taylor,I am 11 years old and my birthday is April 28th.There are 4 people in my family,mom,dad,brother James & myself. My relatives are 7 aunts, 8 uncles, 3 grandparents and 13 cousins. My dad is a driver at M&B Brewery and my mom is a housewife.I have a dog called Mac and 3 fish.My favourite comic is "Suzy",which I read every week. "Carry On"films are very funny and I love to watch them.My favourite book is "The Secret Garden" and I have read it three or four times. I go to 4th Kidderminster St.Mary's and All Saints guides,enjoy dancing and can play the piano. I am on grade 4.I collect stamps and picture cards. I go to St. Ambrose School and will be going to Hagley Roman Catholic School in September 1985.
